{
    solver          PCG;
    preconditioner  DIC;
    tolerance       1e-05;
    relTol          0.1;
}
```

This follows the same pattern as the `p` solver (PCG with DIC preconditioner) but with a more relaxed relative tolerance of 0.1, which is typical for the `epsilon` equation. The `pFinal` entry already uses `$p` to inherit from `p`, so no change is needed there.

